<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/649561-ron">Ron</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">I&apos;m on page 244 and it&apos;s fantastic. It dispels any illusion that our founding fathers and their representative states were united in the direction of <a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">I'm on page 244 and it's fantastic. It dispels any illusion that our founding fathers and their representative states were united in the direction of the country. Even George Washington questioned the longevity of this experiment. Great read and it's nice to find out that there were opposing views and spirited debates during our infancy. Love the soundtrack and looking forward to selling a child to buy tickets to the show.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
</div>
